snippet.textDisplay:
Sheer brilliance. No words.
The way Cello is played, never heard before that instrument can emote like that.
Master Saleem is a master of notes, scales, rhythm ... The extended taan he did there was mind blowing. Once again, when I think of him as the same guy who sang Aahun Aahun ("Love aaj kal", Pritam) and this, you know what I mean. The range is mind boggling.
The little jazz touch on the acoustic gtr solo was so awesome.
Above all, Clinton Cerejo is the real master. This is by far one of the best composition and productions in entire Coke Studio MTV series.
﻿
